snippet.title: Yacht Dice - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Yacht Dice is a classic dice game popular around the world, each player by throwing dice statistics score to carry on the game, the player with the highest score wins. Invite friends to play online, or compete against players from around the world.

Developed by GoodOldMan Studio

#steam #steamgames #steamgame #goodoldmanstudio #yachtdice

FUN FACT: I reviewed this game on InfiniteBacklog in 2022 and I gave it a 6/10. The review link is down below.
https://infinitebacklog.net/users/aklim95/reviews/yacht-dice
